        <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">South America</ENAMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Arawak</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">peoples</ENAMEX> migrated to various <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Caribbean</ENAMEX> islands,
