        The opportunities that the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">island</ENAMEX> had to offer were never
        really exploited by the <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Spanish</ENAMEX>. They were much more interested in the
        <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">gold</ENAMEX> and other treasures to be found in <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">South America</ENAMEX>. However, they
